CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 19, 1961, pg. 15, reads: "Smiling Young Ladies - Shown above are a group of young beauties at the recent Beta Phi Alpha and Alpha Phi Beta dance at Loendi Club...- Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of thirteen men wearing ribbons, posed in Loendi Club for Beta Phi Alpha and Alpha Phi Beta dance
